: lateral and dorsal view of body and full-face view of head (CASENT0249126, Ryan Perry and www.antweb.org); world distribution of 
<taxonomicName box="[932,1080,1767,1789]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Odontoponera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="119" pageNumber="120" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
